## -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
## Distributed Erlang
## -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Name of the node
-name bondy2@127.0.0.1

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie bondy

## Explicit connections only.
-connect_all false

## Connections between hidden nodes and other nodes are not transitive, they must be set up explicitly.
-hidden

## Increase distribution port buffer size.
+zdbbl 32768

## -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
## Erlang
## -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

+sbwt none

## Enabled Time Correction
+c true
+C multi_time_warp

## Max processes
+P 2000000

## Kernel polling
+K true

## Async I/O threads
+A 64


## Finally load the remaining vm.args that are generated by cuttlefish from the
## input provided in the bondy.conf file
-args_file releases/{{release_version}}/generated/vm.generated.args